data.description: Move in and Enjoy! Great location with 80 acre Rum River county park right in your backyard. You will love the Awesome kitchen with corner pantry, granite tops, and stainless appliances. Walk out from your dining to the nice deck for those summer barbecue's. Newer hard surface flooring on upper level along with 3 bedrooms including large master bedroom with walk in closet and private bath. Fantastic large family room in the walk out lower level! There is also another bath with whirlpool tub +4th bedroom. Home also features a heated garage, irrigation system, fenced yard, and extra paved camper/boat parking! Don't miss this one!!
